{"id":99456,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/惊爆眼球的“趣多思”广告（25p）/","date":"2010-08-20T09:19:47Z","modified":"2010-08-20T09:19:47Z","title":"惊爆眼球的“趣多思”广告（25P）","content":"<p><span>广告对创造利润有着至关重要的作用。为了吸引特定受众群体，营销天才们会在静态的影像中寻找灵感，并从中提炼出很酷的广告词。广告代理商们常常靠趣味广告中的幽默来实现这一效果。因此，有趣的构思、有创意的广告词以及巧妙的美术设计和有冲击力的视觉效果，成了必备的元素。</span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/media/print/dhl_chicken_or_egg?size=_original\">DHL &#8211; 鸡还是蛋</a><br />\n<span>DHL：总是最先到达<br />\n<img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"DHL - 鸡还是蛋？\" src=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/files/images/dhlegg.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"DHL - 鸡还是蛋？\" width=\"472\" height=\"334\" /></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Above-the-Influence-Rats-o.jpg\">Above the Influence之老鼠篇</a><br />\n<span>最糟糕的事情莫过于……<br />\nAbove the Influence，美国的禁毒宣传活动，有很多有创意的广告<br />\n<img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Above the Influence Rats\" src=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/11/Above-the-Influence-Rats-o.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Above the Influence Rats\" width=\"672\" height=\"896\" /></span></p>\n<p><span><a href=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/media/print/witte_molen_1?size=_original\">荷兰韦特魔能鸟食（Witte Molen</a>）<br />\n把鸟儿变成人类最好的朋友</span></p>\n<p><img title=\"荷兰韦特魔能鸟食（Witte Molen）\" src=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/files/images/WitteMolen1_DDB&amp;Co.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"荷兰韦特魔能鸟食（Witte Molen）\" /></p>\n<p><span>裸猫（</span><a href=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Without-Clothes-Cat-o.jpg\">Without Clothes Cat</a><span>）<br />\nQueen Bee Waxing做的是脱毛产品<br />\n<img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Without Clothes Cat\" src=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Without-Clothes-Cat-o.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Without Clothes Cat\" width=\"896\" height=\"1120\" /></span></p>\n<p><span>滥竽充数（<a href=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Wannabe-Owl-o.jpg\">Wannabe Owl</a>）<br />\nRutan猫粮，无法抵挡<br />\n<span><img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Wannabe Owl\" src=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Wannabe-Owl-o.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Wannabe Owl\" width=\"960\" height=\"676\" /></span></span></p>\n<p><span>找活儿干（<a href=\"http://www.creativeadawards.com/work-for-food/\">Work For Food</a>）<br />\n杀虫剂广告</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Work For Food\" src=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Work-for-Food-o.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Work For Food\" width=\"960\" height=\"669\" /></p>\n<p><span>狗狗口臭？给它来一块！（<a href=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/media/print/8in1_dental_snacks_bad_dog_breath\">Bad Dog Breath Dental Snacks</a>）</span></p>\n<p><img title=\"Bad Dog Breath Dental Snacks\" src=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/files/images/Lay-cannes09-hund-adsow.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Bad Dog Breath Dental Snacks\" /></p>\n<p><span>碧浪（<a href=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Attack-Crab-o.jpg\">Attack Crab</a>）</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Attack Crab\" src=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Attack-Crab-o.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Attack Crab\" width=\"789\" height=\"546\" /></p>\n<p><span>开塞露？（<a href=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/media/print/kennel1_dog_3\">Fast-working laxatives</a>）</span></p>\n<p><img title=\"Fast-working laxatives\" src=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/files/images/kennel13_0.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Fast-working laxatives\" /></p>\n<p><span>熊（<a href=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/media/print/duende_azul_bear\">Bear</a>）<br />\n穿出更有趣的你（服装广告）</span></p>\n<p><img title=\"Bear\" src=\"http://adsoftheworld.com/files/images/duendeazulbear.jpg\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Bear\" /></p>\n<p><span>东洋章鱼（<a href=\"http://maxcdn.creativeadawards.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/12/Toyo-Octopus-o.jpg\">Toyo Octopus</a>）<br />\n扣人心弦的表演（轮胎广告）</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"border: 0pt none;\" title=\"Toy